longBusinessSummary: Original Sixteen to One Mine, Inc. explores for, produces, and operates gold properties in California. It primarily operates Sixteen to One mine, a hard rock underground gold mine in California. The company holds 25 patented claims in the Alleghany Mining District. Original Sixteen to One Mine, Inc. was founded in 1896 and is based in Alleghany, California.
